WEBVTT

00:09:30.840 --> 00:09:33.416
yes, we were broken,

00:09:33.440 --> 00:09:36.176
and yes, we are numb

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:41.000
and we were silenced
by our own experience.

00:09:43.800 --> 00:09:48.320
It's not just my family.

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:55.096
Rwanda is not the only country

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:58.056
where people have turned on each other

00:09:58.080 --> 00:09:59.520
and murdered each other.